[1.0,"o","\n$ kubectl hpa status api --suggest\n"]
[1.1,"o","HPA default/api\nTarget: Deployment/api\nReplicas: current=10 desired=10 min=2 max=10\nHealth score: 🔴 ScalingLimited 75/100\n\nSummary: HPA is at maxReplicas.\n\nRecommended commands:\n  - Raise maxReplicas: The HPA is capped at maxReplicas=10. Raising it to 20 allows the controller to add capacity if metrics still require it. (risk: medium)\n    $ kubectl patch hpa api -n default --type=merge -p '{\"spec\":{\"maxReplicas\":20}}'\n"]
